input: The project manager leads a team to execute the project within the project's start and end dates. Once the project is created in the project management system, a manager may initiate and later terminate the project due to its completion or for some other reason. The team executes the project. Requirements is the input of a project. As outputs the project shall produce a system. Requirements and systems are work products. Work product has a description, information of the percentage of work completed, and may be validated. The validation is depending on the type of work product. The requirements are validated with users in workshops. System are validated by being tested against the requirements. The requirements may be published using various types of media, including on an intranet or paper form. Systems may be deployed onto specific plataforms.

Once the project is created in the project management system, a manager may initiate and later terminate the project due to its completion or for some other reason. The team executes the project. Work product has a description, information of the percentage of work completed, and may be validated. The validation is depending on the type of work product. The requirements are validated with users in workshops. System are validated by being tested against the requirements. The requirements may be published using various types of media, including on an intranet or paper form. Systems may be deployed onto specific plataforms.
actual_output:
@startuml ProjectManagementSystem

' Work Product and its subclasses
abstract class WorkProduct {
  + description: String
  + percentageCompleted: Float
  + {abstract} validate(): boolean
}

class Requirement {
  + publish(media: String): void
  + validate(): boolean
}

class System {
  + deploy(platform: String): void
  + validate(): boolean
}

WorkProduct <|-- Requirement
WorkProduct <|-- System

' Project related classes
class Project {
  - name: String
  - startDate: Date
  - endDate: Date
  - status: ProjectStatus
  + initiate(): void
  + terminate(reason: String): void
}

class ProjectManager {
  + name: String
  + leadTeam(): void
}

class Team {
  + members: List<Person>
  + executeProject(): void
}

enum ProjectStatus {
  CREATED
  INITIATED
  TERMINATED
  COMPLETED
}

' Relationships
ProjectManager "1" --> "1..*" Team : leads
ProjectManager "1" --> "1..*" Project : manages
Team "1" --> "1..*" Project : executes
Project "1" *-- "1..*" Requirement : has >
Project "1" *-- "1..*" System : produces >

' Validation dependencies
Requirement ..> User : <<depends>> 
System ..> Requirement : <<depends>>

' Supporting classes
class User {
  + name: String
  + role: String
}

class Platform {
  + name: String
  + version: String
}

class Media {
  + type: String
}

' Additional relationships
System --> Platform : deployed on >
Requirement --> Media : published via >

note top of WorkProduct
  Work product has:
  - description
  - percentage of work completed
  - may be validated
  Validation depends on the type
end note

note right of Requirement::validate
  Validated with users
  in workshops
end note

note right of System::validate
  Validated by being tested
  against the requirements
end note

@enduml

@startuml
skinparam handwritten true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

' Abstract Class
abstract class WorkProduct {
  -- Attributes --
  - String description
  - double completionPercentage
  -- Methods --
  + {abstract} validate()
}

' Concrete Classes
class Requirement {
  -- Methods --
  + validateWithUsersInWorkshops()
  + publish()
}

class System {
  -- Methods --
  + testAgainstRequirements()
  + deployOnPlatform()
}

class Project {
  -- Attributes --
  - Date startDate
  - Date endDate
  - String status
  -- Methods --
  + initiate()
  + terminate()
}

class ProjectManager {
  -- Attributes --
  - String name
  - String employeeId
}

class Team {
  -- Attributes --
  - String name
}

class MediaType {
  -- Attributes --
  - String type 'e.g., "Intranet", "Paper Form"'
}

class Platform {
  -- Attributes --
  - String name
  - String type
}

' Inheritance
WorkProduct <|-- Requirement
WorkProduct <|-- System

' Associations
ProjectManager "1" o-- "*" Project : leads >
Team "1" o-- "*" Project : executes >

Project "1" *-- "*" Requirement : has_input >
Project "1" *-- "1" System : produces_output >

Requirement "*" -- "*" MediaType : published_on >
System "*" -- "*" Platform : deployed_on >

' Dependencies
System ..> Requirement : validates_against >
@enduml

@startuml
    class ProjectManager {
        - managerId: string
        - name: string
        - email: string
        + createProject(): Project
        + initiateProject(project: Project): void
        + terminateProject(project: Project): void
        + manageProject(project: Project): void
    }
    
    class ProjectManagementSystem {
        - systemId: string
        - version: string
        + registerProject(project: Project): void
        + trackProgress(): void
        + generateReports(): void
    }
    
    class Project {
        - projectId: string
        - name: string
        - startDate: date
        - endDate: date
        - status: string
        + initiate(): void
        + terminate(): void
        + addRequirement(req: Requirements): void
        + produceSystem(): System
    }
    
    class Team {
        - teamId: string
        - teamName: string
        - size: integer
        + assignToProject(project: Project): void
        + executeProject(): void
    }
    
    abstract class WorkProduct {
        - workProductId: string
        - description: string
        - percentComplete: real
        - creationDate: date
        - lastUpdated: date
        + create(): void
        + update(): void
        + elaborate(): void
        {abstract} validate(): boolean
        + getPercentComplete(): real
    }
    
    class Requirements {
        - requirementType: string
        - priority: string
        + validateWithUsers(): boolean
        + publish(media: Media): void
        + conductWorkshop(workshop: Workshop): void
    }
    
    class System {
        - systemName: string
        - version: string
        - architecture: string
        + validateAgainstRequirements(reqs: Requirements): boolean
        + deploy(platform: Platform): void
        + test(): boolean
    }
    
    class User {
        - userId: string
        - name: string
        - role: string
        + participateInWorkshop(workshop: Workshop): void
        + validateRequirements(req: Requirements): boolean
    }
    
    class Workshop {
        - workshopId: string
        - date: date
        - duration: integer
        - location: string
        + conductSession(): void
        + gatherFeedback(): void
    }
    
    class Media {
        - mediaType: string
        - format: string
        + publishContent(content: string): void
    }
    
    class Platform {
        - platformId: string
        - platformName: string
        - environment: string
        - specifications: string
        + deploySystem(system: System): void
        + supportDeployment(): boolean
    }
    
    ' Inheritance relationships
    WorkProduct <|-- Requirements
    WorkProduct <|-- System
    
    ' Composition and Aggregation relationships
    ProjectManager "1" *-- "0..*" Project : manages
    ProjectManager "1" --> "1" Team : leads
    Project "1" --> "1" ProjectManagementSystem : created_in
    Project "1" *-- "1..*" Requirements : uses_as_input
    Project "1" *-- "1" System : produces_as_output
    
    ' Association relationships
    Requirements "0..*" --> "0..*" User : validated_by
    Requirements "0..*" --> "0..*" Workshop : validated_in
    User "1..*" --> "0..*" Workshop : participates_in
    System "1" --> "1..*" Requirements : tested_against
    Requirements "0..*" --> "0..*" Media : published_using
    System "0..*" --> "0..*" Platform : deployed_on
    
    ' Team execution relationship
    Team "1" --> "1" Project : executes
@enduml
